
David G. cheat sheet
	http://docutils.sourceforge.net/docs/user/rst/cheatsheet.txt

Links
	regular ref
		Reference_
		`two words`_
	target:
		heading names (implicit target)
		.. _two words: (explicit target but following para is actually referred to) 
		.. _Python: http://www.python.org/  (explicit external target)
		_`inline target`
	Anonymous references
		ref & target texts differ, target is next '__'
			`Anonymous reference is here`__
			__reference
		target is also a ref
			__reference_

Terms & Definitions

	Term [: classifier]
		Definition para two


Bullets
	eg

	- A bullet list

	  + Nested bullet list.
	  + Nested item 2.

Numbering
	#. List items may be auto-enumerated.

Directives
	syntax
		.. name:: <title or text>
			:field: <value text>

	eg
		.. contents:: Table of Contents
		.. section-numbering::


		.. image:: image.jpg
			:alt: alt text
			:target: ref_

        .. class:: classname
            applies to: anyelement
            use for: css style selector
        

        "class" option of directives that support it:

        .. topic:: Extra Material For Handouts
           :class: handout



Comments
	syntax
		.. Comment here etc.
		   Align text
		
Fields
	:fieldname:	field body - will wrap

	:field arg1 arg2:
		field body



